OL,3,CDad who completed 365 marathons in 365
OL,4,Cdays 'surprised' to be made MBE
OL,6,FA father of three who completed 365
OL,7,Fmarathons in as many days has said it
OL,8,Fwas a "real surprise" to be made an
OL,9,FMBE.
OL,11,FWest Cumbrian Gary McKee achieved the
OL,12,Ffeat while working full-time in 2022
OL,13,Fand raised more than #1.3 million for
OL,14,Fcharity in the process.
OL,16,FThe nuclear plant worker then ran 100
OL,17,Fmarathons in 100 days in 2026,
OL,18,Fculminating in the London Marathon.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
