CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1782488897
OL,3,CDad who completed 365 marathons in 365
OL,4,Cdays 'surprised' to be made MBE
OL,6,FHe was honoured as a Member of the
OL,7,FOrder of the British Empire by the
OL,8,FPrince of Wales on Wednesday.
OL,10,FIn a statement after the Windsor
OL,11,FCastle ceremony, Mr McKee, from
OL,12,FCleator Moor said: "It was a real
OL,13,Fsurprise and a huge honour to be
OL,14,Frecognised with an MBE, today was
OL,15,Fincredibly special.
OL,17,F"To receive the award from Prince
OL,18,FWilliam at Windsor Castle is something
OL,19,FI never imagined would happen.
OL,26,@tD@TOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1782488897
OL,3,CDad who completed 365 marathons in 365
OL,4,Cdays 'surprised' to be made MBE
OL,6,F"Fundraising has always been about
OL,7,Fmaking a difference and supporting
OL,8,Fcauses that mean a lot to me, and so
OL,9,Fmany others, so being recognised in
OL,10,Fthis way is very humbling."
OL,12,FIn April, Mr McKee told the Press
OL,13,FAssociation that he has clocked more
OL,14,Fthan 33,000 miles on his Strava
OL,15,Fprofile ` more than the circumference
OL,16,Fof the Earth, which is 24,900 miles.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
