CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1782488897
OL,3,CDad who completed 365 marathons in 365
OL,4,Cdays 'surprised' to be made MBE
OL,6,FThis was despite not "using it for
OL,7,Fthat many years", he said, adding:
OL,8,F"You could probably double that for
OL,9,Fthe things I've done, so it's a long
OL,10,Fway.
OL,12,F"I'm on my second lap of running
OL,13,Faround the Earth."
OL,15,FHis MBE is for services to charity and
OL,16,Fthe Cleator Moor community and Mr
OL,17,FMcKee said sharing the ceremony with
OL,18,Fhis family "made the day even more
OL,19,Fspecial."
OL,26,@nD@VOUoD@PO]pD@AOUtD@AOUuD@RO]zD@LOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
