PN,32606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1782488897
OL,3,CDad who completed 365 marathons in 365
OL,4,Cdays 'surprised' to be made MBE
OL,6,FHe said he is "proud" to have
OL,7,Frepresented West Cumbria and hopes the
OL,8,FMBE will help "shine a light on the
OL,9,Fincredible generosity, community
OL,10,Fspirit and kindness that exists back
OL,11,Fhome".
OL,13,FMr McKee ran from Land's End to John
OL,14,FO'Groats in 2011, covering 874 miles.
OL,16,FHe has also completed the Coast to
OL,17,FCoast challenge of 116 miles in under
OL,18,F24 hours.
OL,26,@nD@OOUnD@UO]pD@OOUsD@EO]
